{{vgname|超級瑪利歐賽車|ja=スーパーマリオカート|en=Super Mario Kart|cn=超级马力欧卡丁车|aka-cn=超级马里奥赛车|tw=超級瑪利歐賽車|aka-hk=超級瑪利奧賽車|hk=tw}}是[[任天堂情报开发本部|任天堂情报开发本部]]开发的[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]，並于[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]平台发行。这是[[瑪利歐賽車系列|瑪利歐賽車系列]]首作，于1992年8月在日本首发，同年9月在北美发行，翌年1月在欧洲发行<ref name="SMK Review">{{cite web|title=Review: Super Mario Kart (Wii U eShop / Super NES)|publisher=Nintendo Life|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/wiiu-eshop/super_mario_kart_snes|first=Jamie|last=O'Neill|date=2014-03-28|accessdate=2014-07-03|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012093510/http://www.nintendolife.com/reviews/wiiu-eshop/super_mario_kart_snes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏全球销量876万，为第四[[畅销超级任天堂游戏列表|畅销超级任天堂游戏]]。《超級瑪利歐賽車》于2009和2010年在[[Wii|Wii]]的[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]再版<ref name="JP VC">{{cite web|title=Virtual Console バーチャルコンソール|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/vc_mk/index.html|language=ja|accessdate=2008-07-14|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317114053/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/vc_mk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NA VC">{{cite web |url=https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/O-6Hu5sS3KndAbl1v6fJElEIDoveAwhn |title=Download New BIT.TRIP Kicks, Speeding Karts, Magic Castles and More |date=2009-11-23|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]] |accessdate=2009-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126024620/http://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/O-6Hu5sS3KndAbl1v6fJElEIDoveAwhn |archive-date=2009-11-26 |dead-url=yes |language=en}}</ref><ref name="EU VC">{{cite web |last=East |first=Thomas |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/article.php?id=16217 |title=Super Mario Kart coming to Virtual Console this Friday |date=2010-03-29|publisher=[[官方任天堂杂志|官方任天堂杂志]] |accessdate=2010-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426192958/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/16217/super-mario-kart-coming-to-virtual-console-this-friday/# |archive-date=2012-04-26 |dead-url=yes |df= |language=en}}</ref>；2013和2014年在[[Wii_U|Wii U]] Virtual Console再版。

《超級瑪利歐賽車》获得积极评价，在呈现、革新和[[Mode_7|Mode 7]]图形的应用上获得称赞<ref name="NMS">{{cite journal|title=Super NES Review - Super Mario Kart|journal=[[官方任天堂杂志|官方任天堂杂志]]|volume=1|pages=20–24|publisher=EMAP|url=http://www.meanmachinesmag.co.uk/pdf/supermariokartsnes.pdf?PHPSESSID=8de0bbed3648828556a66b0145ad1041|accessdate=2008-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2008-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905080730/http://www.meanmachinesmag.co.uk/pdf/supermariokartsnes.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="1up ess50">{{cite web|last=Hirandand |first=Ravi |title=The Essential 50 #29 |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3134033 |accessdate=2008-12-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sD3Kr6UX?url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3134033 |archivedate=2010-08-24 |language=en}}</ref>。游戏入选《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》、[[IGN|IGN]]、《[[The_Age|The Age]]》等组织评予的史上最佳游戏榜单，[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]亦称其为史上最佳[[游戏机游戏|游戏机游戏]]<ref name="IGN 100-07">{{cite web|title=IGN's 100 top games Of All Time 2007|website=IGN|year=2007|url=http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_23.html|access-date=2008-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414133232/http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_23.html|archive-date=2012-04-14|language=en}}</ref><ref name="edge100">{{cite web|title=Edges's Top 100 Games of All Time |publisher=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] |date=2007-07-02 |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/edges-top-100-games-all-time |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080822053639/http://www.edge-online.com/magazine/edges-top-100-games-of-all-time?page=0%2C8 |archivedate=2008-08-22 |accessdate=2008-12-28 |deadurl=yes|language=en }}</ref><ref name="age">{{cite web|last=Hill|first=Jason|title=The 50 best games|publisher=[[The_Age|The Age]]|date=2005-06-10|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/livewire/the-50-best-games/2005/10/04/1128191720699.html|accessdate=2008-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2008-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209221355/http://www.theage.com.au/news/livewire/the-50-best-games/2005/10/04/1128191720699.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GS ggoat">{{cite web|last=Navarro|first=Alex|title=The Greatest Games of All Time: Super Mario Kart|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/6136230/index.html?tag=result;title;4|accessdate=2008-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2012-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108064044/http://www.gamespot.com/features/the-greatest-games-of-all-time-super-mario-kart-6136230/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NGen21">{{cite magazine|last=|first= |title=Top 100 Games of All Time |magazine=[[次世代_(雜誌)|次世代]]|issue=21 |publisher={{Tsl|en|Imagine Media}} |date=1996-09|page=56|language=en}}</ref><ref name="guinness50">{{cite web|last=Ivan|first=Tom|title=Guinness ranks top 50 games of all time|publisher=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|date=2009-02-28|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=209385|accessdate=2009-03-14|language=en|archive-date=2013-06-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HYGYdHnM?url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/209385/guinness-ranks-top-50-games-of-all-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。游戏常被称为卡丁车竞速子类游戏的缔造者，其他开发商亦企图复制它的成功。本作亦成为马里奥系列往非[[平台游戏|平台游戏]]扩展的关键，该系列的多样化亦称为史上最畅销的游戏系列<ref name="GS ggoat" /><ref name="Sutra M#1">{{cite web|last=Jenkins|first=David|title=Mario Tops Best Selling Game Franchise List|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=2007-01-10|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12349|accessdate=2009-01-01|language=en|archive-date=2008-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617160750/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=12349|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《超級瑪利歐賽車》在[[家用游戏机|家用游戏机]]、[[掌上游戏机|掌上游戏机]]和[[街机|街机]]上的续作皆获得媒体好评和商业成功。《超級瑪利歐賽車》中玩法的核心元素，也在系列後續作品中完整保留了下来<ref name="1UP retronaut">{{cite web|last=Parish|first=Jeremy|author2=Bob Mackey|title=Retronauts Crashes Into Mario Kart|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|date=2008-04-10|url=http://www.1up.com/news/retronauts-crashes-mario-kart|accessdate=2008-12-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110523081901/http://www.1up.com/news/retronauts-crashes-mario-kart|archivedate=2011-05-23|language=en|df=}}</ref>。

==玩法==
《超級瑪利歐賽車》可供單人或多人遊玩，本作具有「大獎賽」、「計時賽<ref name="ndojo">{{cite web|title=Reviews - Super Mario Kart|url=http://www.nintendojo.com/reviews/SNES/view_item.php?1052508795|accessdate=2008-12-28|last=Heckel|first=Nathan|publisher=Nintendojo|language=en|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061114022502/http://www.nintendojo.com/reviews/SNES/view_item.php?1052508795|archive-date=2006-11-14}}</ref>」與「氣球對戰<ref name="ndojo" />」可供遊玩。

在遊戲中，玩家共有來自[[瑪利歐系列|瑪利歐系列]]中的八種角色可供選擇，玩家可選擇其中一位進行遊戲<ref name="npower">{{cite journal|title=Super Mario Kart|date=1992-10|journal=[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂]]|volume=41|pages=83–91|language=en}}</ref>，於具有瑪利歐系列要素的賽道上奔馳，本作的賽道主題大多来自《[[超級瑪利歐世界|超級瑪利歐世界]]》。大獎賽共有四種獎盃、每種含有5個賽道，總計有20種不同的賽道。氣球模式中則有4種對戰專用賽道<ref name="npower" /><ref name="SMK">{{cite video game| title = 超級瑪利歐賽車| developer = [[任天堂情報開發本部|任天堂情報開發本部]]| publisher = [[任天堂|任天堂]]| date = 1992-08-27| platform = [[超級任天堂|超級任天堂]]}}</ref>。

遊戲與眾不同的引入了道具機制，玩家可以透過獲得的道具使用各種不同的能力，讓競賽更加具有變化性。

==制作==
《超級瑪利歐賽車》由[[宫本茂|宫本茂]]制作，{{Tsl|ja|杉山直_(ゲームクリエイター)|杉山直}}和[[绀野秀树|绀野秀树]]担任总监<ref>{{cite video game| title = 超級瑪利歐賽車| developer = [[任天堂情報開發本部|任天堂情報開發本部]]| publisher = [[任天堂|任天堂]]| date = 1992-08-27| platform = [[超級任天堂|超級任天堂]]| scene=開發人員清單}}</ref>。

本作到的一点是，《超級瑪利歐賽車》使用了[[Mode_7|Mod 7]]圖形渲染技術，也曾技術先前也於《[[F-Zero|F-Zero]]》中使用
